---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - BuildPrivacyPolicy" description="Terms of service for BuildPrivacyPolicy.com. Read about your responsibilities, our disclaimers, and how the free privacy policy generator works.">

<div class="sticky-header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <a href="/" class="logo-link">
      <svg class="logo-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 128 128" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="128" height="128" rx="28" fill="#1E3A5F"/><path d="M64 24C64 24 40 34 32 38V62C32 82 46 98 64 104C82 98 96 82 96 62V38C88 34 64 24 64 24Z" fill="#2E5A8F" stroke="#5B9BD5" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M52 64L60 72L78 54" stroke="white" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      <span class="logo-text">BuildPrivacyPolicy</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-container">
  <div class="page-card">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By using BuildPrivacyPolicy ("the Service"), you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p>

    <h2>Description of Service</h2>
    <p>BuildPrivacyPolicy is a free tool that generates privacy policies based on answers you provide about your app or service. The Service is provided by <strong>HorizonTD</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Not Legal Advice</h2>
    <p>The Service is <strong>not</strong> a law firm, and the generated content does <strong>not</strong> constitute legal advice. The privacy policies and other documents generated by this tool are created based solely on the information you provide. We are not lawyers, and this Service is not a substitute for professional legal counsel.</p>
    <p>You must review and verify any generated policy with a qualified legal professional before using it. You are solely responsible for ensuring your privacy policy accurately reflects your app's data practices and complies with all applicable laws, regulations, and platform requirements.</p>

    <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
    <p>You are responsible for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Providing accurate and complete information about your app's data practices</li>
      <li>Reviewing the generated policy for accuracy before publishing</li>
      <li>Consulting a qualified legal professional to ensure legal compliance</li>
      <li>Keeping your privacy policy updated when your app's data practices change</li>
      <li>Using the Service in compliance with applicable laws</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>No Warranties</h2>
    <p>The Service is provided <strong>"as is"</strong> and <strong>"as available"</strong> without any warranties of any kind, whether express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or legal compliance.</p>
    <p>We make no representations or warranties that:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The generated policies will satisfy legal requirements in any jurisdiction</li>
      <li>The generated content will be accurate, complete, or up to date</li>
      <li>The Service will be uninterrupted or error-free</li>
      <li>The Service will meet your specific requirements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, HorizonTD and its operators shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenue, whether incurred directly or indirectly, or any loss of data, use, goodwill, or other intangible losses resulting from your use of the Service.</p>

    <h2>Changes to the Service</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the Service (or any part thereof) at any time, with or without notice. We shall not be liable to you or any third party for any modification, suspension, or discontinuation of the Service.</p>

    <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page. Your continued use of the Service after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

    <h2>Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Republic of Turkey, without regard to conflict of law principles.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:ozandikbas@gmail.com">ozandikbas@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .sticky-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: white;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .header-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .logo-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .logo-link:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .logo-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .logo-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }
  .page-container {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 16px 80px;
  }
  .page-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }
  .page-card h1 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #9CA3AF;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .page-card h2 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .page-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .page-card ul {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }
  .page-card li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .page-card a {
    color: #2563EB;
  }
  .page-card strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
